title: #92Noon! Boudreau/Nestor/Florio/Numbers/Gleeman
description: Full show! Wild coach Bruce Boudreau opens the show, Baltimore radio's Nestor Aparicio gives us intel on the new kicker, then Florio's weekly hit closes the first hour. Vikings numbers game takes us from 91-99, then Aaron Gleeman is in studio for the entire final hour!
